sentence: In early trading on Thursday, shares of Walt Disney ( DIS ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 2.0%.
Year to date, Walt Disney registers a 0.8% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is JPMorgan Chase ( JPM ), trading down 1.1%.
JPMorgan Chase is showing a gain of 1.7% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ), trading down 0.9%, and UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ), trading up 1.1% on the day.
